OL,17,Fwarned Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,18,FNetanyahu that continued US support
OL,19,Ffor Israel's war against Hamas would
OL,20,Fbe dependent on protection measures
OL,21,Ffor civilians and aid workers.
