OL,6,FMilitary spokespeople said that under
OL,7,Fthe Israeli army's rules of
OL,8,Fengagement, officers must have more
OL,9,Fthan one reason for identifying
OL,10,Fsomeone as a target before they can be
OL,11,Fhit, but this investigation determined
OL,12,Fthat a colonel had authorised the
OL,13,Fseries of deadly drone strikes on the
OL,14,Fconvoy based on one major's
OL,15,Fobservation.
